#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/project_bin_use.rst:63
msgid ""
"Search field to :ref:`search for assets<project_bin_use_searching>` in the "
"bin"
msgstr ""
"Camp de cerca per a :ref:`cercar recursos<project_bin_use_searching>` a la "
"safata"

