#: ../../project_and_asset_management/project_bin/project_bin_use.rst:95
msgid ""
"Click on the |application-menu|\\ :guilabel:`Options` icon and use the "
"slider or the buttons to the left or right of it to increase or decrease the"
" zoom level."
msgstr ""
"Feu clic a la icona |application-menu|\\ :guilabel:`Opcions` i empreu el "
"control lliscant o els botons a la seva esquerra o dreta per a augmentar o "
